          class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white border-2 border-white rounded-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-green-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 transform"
        >
          <span>Nous contacter</span>
